{
  "stem": "935.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And at no time until you were driven into Avenue Louise could you have sensed this whole thing is-- why?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What for, all this-- this-- this incredible scheme?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Didn't make sense, did it?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Max was there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was standing right there, next to the German Nazi.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Didn't say a word as we walked by.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Much later, I found out about him from people in the first camp in Belgium; that he was, of course, Jewish.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They knew him from synagogues, where he was there too, with others.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there was one day when they picked up a lot of people-- a lot of Jews-- he was among them.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And while most of the others were never seen again or heard from again, he walked around very free.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And as one of the ladies in the camp said, I hope he knows God real good.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He has a lot of explaining to do when this is over.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So Max was one of them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the strange thing is there was a time in the train, shortly before we got to Belgium, when I was sitting there, that a man on a platform, like in a bad movie-- in a trench coat, up, you know, was-- kept making signs to me.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I said, what-- what kind of a thing is this?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "John was sitting right next to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was asleep.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Why would he wave me out?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was-- I didn't know what he wanted.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was definitely making signs to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I finally woke John and I said, hey, what is this?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he picked me up with all the others, said go, go, go, go.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we ran to other wagons.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
